  "3026000": {
    "name": "破碎空间旅行者",
    "steam_appid": 3026000,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎各位玩家加入官方讨论群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：942540362 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discord：Broken Space Traveler </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一场跨越维度的冒险，来自不同空间的旅人，在破碎的空间里探寻无尽的秘密。在这个神秘的世界里，你需要收集各种道具来强化自身，升级武器，并在危机四伏的环境中存活下来。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色亮点：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多元角色，策略生存：</strong>数十位拥有独特机制的旅人等待你的召唤，每位旅人都拥有其独特的生存之道，选择最适合你的角色，制定你的生存策略吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/174785878e9afa4b88de3498f594613c.webp?t=1731376352\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/174785878e9afa4b88de3498f594613c.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=450 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>道具组合，无限可能：</strong>海量道具任你挑选，自由组合，创造出属于你的独特玩法。每一次组合都是全新的体验，让你的冒险之旅充满无限可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/ac54c5e2db095396812712daa75e5e60.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/ac54c5e2db095396812712daa75e5e60.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/ac54c5e2db095396812712daa75e5e60.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>武器升级，形态多变</strong>：数十种武器等你来解锁，每把武器都拥有三个独特的升级分支，不同的升级路径将赋予武器不同的力量。做出你的选择，打造属于你的最强武器！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/70ad2dda3b7b1237d79ab3be16d2cd7b.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/70ad2dda3b7b1237d79ab3be16d2cd7b.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/70ad2dda3b7b1237d79ab3be16d2cd7b.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>强化旅人，满足需求：</strong>通过收集道具或触发事件，可以强化你的旅人，满足武器的升级需求。在探索的过程中不断提升自身实力，成为破碎空间的王者！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/b7076b05e80a82e2eb7b2cf2c37bd353.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/b7076b05e80a82e2eb7b2cf2c37bd353.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/b7076b05e80a82e2eb7b2cf2c37bd353.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁空间，调整策略：</strong>在破碎的空间中存活，你将逐渐解锁更加完整的破碎空间。不同的空间拥有不同的环境和挑战，调整你的策略，迎接新的冒险吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/29de809d40baa789da9192247dbddf84.poster.avif?t=1731376352\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/29de809d40baa789da9192247dbddf84.webm?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026000/extras/29de809d40baa789da9192247dbddf84.mp4?t=1731376352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即加入《破碎空间旅行者》，开启你的跨维度冒险之旅！</p>",
